ing of TTCF protein. The experimental in\nvivo immunisation data confirms the retention of immunogenicity after release\nfrom silica. Our results suggest that we could utilise this technology for\nmulticomponent vaccines, therapeutics or other biopharmaceuticals that are not\ncompatible with lyophilisation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Nov 2018 16:29:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-09"}
