complete HMMs in a smoothed\nanalysis model.\n  3. Higher order tensor decompositions, where we generalize the so-called\nFOOBI algorithm of Cardoso to find order-$\\ell$ rank-one tensors in a subspace.\nThis allows us to obtain polynomially robust decomposition algorithms for\n$2\\ell$'th order tensors with rank $O(n^{\\ell})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Nov 2018 18:12:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Apr 2019 02:12:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-25"}
