o plasmonic\nbranches on the interlayer separation is not affected by temperature at long\nwavelengths; the acoustic mode energy varies slightly with increasing the\ninterlayer distance, whereas the optical mode remains unchanged.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Nov 2018 13:49:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-07"}
